data.description: Welcome to this very well maintained 3 bedroom 2.5 bath, 2-story corner unit townhome! This townhouse features new 2023 hurricane impact windows & doors, 2023 tankless water heater, 2yr old A/c unit, 2023 break box, tile floors throughout, spacious bedrooms with 3 closets in the master bedroom & a walk-in closet in a guest room. There is a beautiful fully fenced & partially covered back patio with New 2023 hurricane impact siding glass doors  & a built in BBQ area, Great for entertaining! Located only minutes away from all major highways(595, 95 & the Turnpike), the local colleges as well as shopping and dinning!! This is a must see!!
